grade_evaluation.en:
The course exam for this course will be composed of completed assessments, the components of which will have the following weighting:
*	written assignments - 50%;
*	seminar presentations - 30%;
*	teamwork (development ideas for a proposed new wellness centre) - 20%.
Requirements for sitting or resitting the assessments will be established by the teaching staff member responsible for the course in accordance with the Study Regulations.

